FBIS3-56905 "drsov014_f_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 National Affairs Kravchuk Fires Representative in Ternopol Oblast LD2001204694 Kiev UT-1 Television Network in Ukrainian 1700 GMT 20 Jan 94 LD2001204694 Kiev UT-1 Television Network Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Text] We have just received a decree of the president of Ukraine, which says that Roman Hronyak, representative of the president of Ukraine in Ternopol Oblast, has been released from his post for gross violations of labor discipline. (Bohdan Andrushkin), first deputy head of Ternopol Oblast state administration, has been charged with carrying out those duties.
